                     move  w-all-str-cat (2)
                                          to   w-exe-alf-pro          .
       ext-prm-ass-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     ext-prm-ass-999.
       ext-prm-ass-999.
           exit.

